15
00:02:02.466 --> 00:02:07.739
Wikipedia is critical because it ranks at the top of Google and other search engines.

16
00:02:07.739 --> 00:02:15.059
When investors, journalists, or employees search for Pfizer, the Wikipedia article is often the first link they click.

17
00:02:15.059 --> 00:02:20.208
This view tracks pageview trends, maintenance flags, and editorial recommendations.

18
00:02:20.208 --> 00:02:26.411
Important: Wikipedia is an open-source platform — it cannot be updated or edited by Pfizer directly.

19
00:02:26.411 --> 00:02:30.567
Changes must come from the volunteer community that runs Wikipedia.

20
00:02:30.567 --> 00:02:39.066
For additional insights and strategy regarding your presence on Wikipedia, please contact Vibe Code Flow for more information and advice.

21
00:02:39.421 --> 00:02:46.227
