22
00:02:46.227 --> 00:02:52.264
As with the corporate article, only the Wikipedia community can edit the page, not the company itself.

23
00:02:52.264 --> 00:02:58.241
Vibe Code Flow can help you interpret these signals and plan the right community engagement strategy.

